1116ae62-9a98-4740-aba0-1790c4b3258e.name: deployement.environment
1116ae62-9a98-4740-aba0-1790c4b3258e.queryValue:
SELECT DISTINCT(JSONExtractString(labels, 'deployment_environment')) as deployment_environment
FROM signoz_metrics.time_series_v4
WHERE (metric_name LIKE '%otelcol%')
GROUP BY deployment_environment

20076cba-98bf-4248-9f27-38e76ae3343d.name: region
